{"tid":103630,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"其實人工只係一個相對的概念","createTime":"2017-02-01T12:59:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-02T09:01:03.000Z","uid":41265,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a26f48580cba6212fe56e62b9ff314ede6192bbc","tid":103630,"uid":41265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T12:59:02.000Z","msg":"成日諗第時要每個月搵幾多錢先夠<br />\n但係其實小有小用大有大用<br />\n每個月嘅支出離唔開衣食住行<br />\n着咁多食咁多住咁多行咁多<br />\n可能只是質素上分別<br />\n平民食物一樣好食<br />\n要靚衫唔一定要名牌<br />\n住500尺同5000尺都係瞓覺沖涼屙屎睇電視<br />\n揸豐田同揸法拉利都係有限速<br />\n係咪真係人工越高越好?"},{"pid":"202325c5dc6263c75aef915e9755c14152d1e0d2","tid":103630,"uid":44958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T13:04:56.000Z","msg":"知足常樂咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"081f2cbaa33ae8f9e9106e8a469ddf2c821bbcbd","tid":103630,"uid":59047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T13:14:45.000Z","msg":"而家係住50呎迫地鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁不如去訓街，租都唔駛俾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"286619ecf4e8a96abede3a8b2c35de6975c8d78d","tid":103630,"uid":64131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T13:22:07.000Z","msg":"夠錢退休？"},{"pid":"e98436c8c031362d4d6d74d59d623920a9d51edf","tid":103630,"uid":49487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T13:28:06.000Z","msg":"社交<br />\n有病/失業應急<br />\n退休"},{"pid":"3b300f548a9d6000792213846372f5b68c5b215b","tid":103630,"uid":55458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T13:36:15.000Z","msg":"自欺欺人"},{"pid":"33f8772227173070b6d15c2c931b1f104ce8259c","tid":103630,"uid":68993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T13:38:58.000Z","msg":"少年.....你"},{"pid":"fe6cbc31039aeeda65fc71652b4f5b4f07be9a58","tid":103630,"uid":7343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T13:40:57.000Z","msg"